@startuml Purchase_Management_Sequence
autonumber

skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam ParticipantPadding 10
skinparam defaultFontSize 20
skinparam maxMessageSize 400

actor "Admin Toko / Sistem" as Admin
boundary "UI Kelola Pembelian" as UI
control "Purchase Controller" as Controller
database "DB" as DB

== 1. Input Pembelian Baru ==
Admin -> UI : Masukkan nota supplier & list item
UI -> Controller : Simpan data pembelian barang
activate Controller
Controller -> DB : Simpan rincian nota pembelian
Controller -> DB : Perbarui stok produk & hitung ulang HPP (Weighted Average)
DB --> UI : Konfirmasi Berhasil (Stok & HPP Terupdate)
deactivate Controller

== 2. Edit / Pembatalan (Reversal) ==
Admin -> UI : Ubah atau Hapus Nota Pembelian
note right: Memerlukan penyesuaian stok & HPP (Weighted Average Reversal)

alt Aksi: Edit Nota
    UI -> Controller : Ubah data pembelian
    Controller -> DB : Kembalikan kondisi stok & HPP sebelumnya
    Controller -> DB : Terapkan data & hitung ulang HPP baru
else Aksi: Taruh di Trash (Archive)
    UI -> Controller : Request pengarsipan data pembelian
    Controller -> DB : Kembalikan stok/HPP & pindahkan ke arsip sampah
end

Controller --> UI : Konfirmasi Berhasil
@enduml